@startuml seq-request-access
!theme plain
title Sequence — Bác sĩ yêu cầu truy cập hồ sơ (3 bước)

actor Doctor
participant "DoctorMobile" as DM
participant "Backend\n+ Relayer" as Backend
participant "EHRSystemSecure" as EHR
participant "ConsentLedger" as Consent
participant "PatientMobile" as PM
actor Patient

== Bước 1: Doctor yêu cầu (gas tự trả) ==

Doctor -> DM : Mở RequestAccess\npaste cidHash\nchọn RequestType
DM -> EHR : requestAccess(patient, cidHash,\ntype, deadline)\n[doctor signs + pays gas]
EHR -> EHR : _requests[reqId] = {...}
EHR -> EHR : emit AccessRequested

EHR --> Backend : event indexed by subgraph
Backend -> Backend : sync AccessRequest table
Backend -> PM : Expo push:\n"Bác sĩ X yêu cầu hồ sơ Y"

== Bước 2: Patient phê duyệt (sponsored) ==

PM -> Patient : Mở RequestsScreen\n+ biometric MFA gate
Patient -> PM : Bấm Phê duyệt\n+ vân tay
PM -> PM : sign ApprovePermit (EIP-712)
PM -> Backend : POST /api/relayer/approve-request\n{reqId, signature}
Backend -> EHR : approveRequestBySig(...)\n(sponsored)
EHR -> Consent : grantInternal(patient,\ndoctor, cidHash, ...)
Consent -> Consent : emit ConsentGranted
EHR -> EHR : emit RequestCompleted

== Bước 2b (alternate): Patient từ chối ==

Patient -> PM : Bấm Từ chối\n+ vân tay
PM -> PM : sign RejectPermit (EIP-712)
PM -> Backend : POST /api/relayer/reject-request\n{reqId, signature, reason?}
Backend -> EHR : rejectRequestBySig(...)\n(sponsored — Wave K)
EHR -> EHR : emit RequestRejected
Backend -> Backend : mirror status='rejected'\n+ rejectionReason off-chain

== Bước 3: Doctor claim + decrypt ==

Backend --> DM : Socket.io push\n"consent:updated"
DM -> Backend : GET /api/key-share/my
Backend --> DM : KeyShare row (encryptedPayload)
DM -> Backend : GET /api/key-share/record/:cidHash
Backend -> Consent : canAccess(patient,\ndoctor, cidHash)
Consent --> Backend : true
Backend --> DM : encryptedPayload (NaCl box)
DM -> DM : decrypt NaCl box → AES key\nthen decrypt ciphertext (IPFS)
DM -> Doctor : Render record

@enduml
